that I've ever read, that a
woman of that era would have...

272
00:24:39.954 --> 00:24:42.749
the strength to reject Darcy
when he treated her poorly.

273
00:24:42.874 --> 00:24:43.875
That's a load.

274
00:24:47.754 --> 00:24:50.965
