Okay? I have a boyfriend.

292
00:25:35.009 --> 00:25:39.347
Us... I thought we were talking
about Pride and Prejudice.

293
00:25:46.813 --> 00:25:50.817
Hey, do you want to
go get some coffee?

294
00:25:50.942 --> 00:25:53.111
How can someone be so arrogant?

295
00:25:53.236 --> 00:25:55.655
"Elizabeth Bennett
needs to chill."

296
00:25:55.780 --> 00:25:59.951
Like who even...
who even says that?

297
00:26:00.034 --> 00:26:02.662
That's just Hardin
being Hardin.

298
00:26:02.787 --> 00:26:04.164
You know him?

299
00:26:04.289 --> 00:26:09.461
Yeah, we're, uh, we're
practically related.

300
00:26:09.544 --> 00:26:13.506
My mom is dating
Chancellor Scott.

301
00:26:13.631 --> 00:26:16.968
Chancellor Scott
is Hardin's dad...

302
00:26:17.051 --> 00:26:21.556
and Hardin and I, we tolerate
each other, but barely.

303
00:26:21.639 --> 00:26:24.434
His father's the chancellor?

304
00:26:24.517 --> 00:26:25.894
Yeah.

305
00:26:29.564 --> 00:26:33.318
Listen, Tessa, he's just
trying to get a reaction.

306
00:26:33.443 --> 00:26:36.654
Well, he's not gonna
get one from me.

307
00:26:36.780 --> 00:26:39.783
Hm...

308
00:26:43.536 --> 00:26:45.747
Agh!

309
00:26:45.830 --> 00:26:47.415
It actually does hurt.

310
00:26:50.001 --> 00:26:51.336
You should get one.

311
00:26:52.670 --> 00:26:55.256
My mom would literally kill me.

312
00:26:55.340 --> 00:26:56.716
You need to get this.

313
00:27:00.595 --> 00:27:02.138
I bet you'd love that one.

314
00:27:02.222 --> 00:27:05.016
Yeah, dice...

315
00:27:05.100 --> 00:27:07.769
I feel like my mom has
everything planned out for me.

316
00:27:07.852 --> 00:27:11.189
Like, I think she's been
planning my wedding

