Wait, is Noah the only dude
you've ever gone out with?

319
00:27:20.865 --> 00:27:22.784
That's sad.

320
00:27:26.955 --> 00:27:28.164
Ooh, ow!

321
00:27:28.248 --> 00:27:29.999
Watch it.

322
00:27:30.083 --> 00:27:33.545
Yeah, you guys really
aren't selling me on this.

323
00:27:41.511 --> 00:27:46.057
Ssh! You
look so good tonight.

324
00:27:46.891 --> 00:27:48.893
Shh!

325
00:28:16.337 --> 00:28:18.423
Can I get a
small coffee, please?

326
00:28:25.972 --> 00:28:27.807
Here you go.

327
00:28:27.932 --> 00:28:29.434
Yeah, thanks.

328
00:28:42.322 --> 00:28:45.450
- Hi.
- Hi.

329
00:28:45.533 --> 00:28:47.619
I can't stay away from you.

330
00:28:50.413 --> 00:28:52.457
What?

331
00:28:52.540 --> 00:28:55.376
Well, we're gonna
see each other.

332
00:28:55.460 --> 00:28:58.421
I'm friends with Steph
and you're roommates.

333
00:29:01.674 --> 00:29:05.095
Tessa, let's just start over,
