335
00:29:07.472 --> 00:29:09.140
Why not?

336
00:29:12.394 --> 00:29:14.145
I want to show you something.

337
00:29:14.229 --> 00:29:16.856
So show me then.

338
00:29:16.981 --> 00:29:19.776
It's a... it's a place.

339
00:29:21.444 --> 00:29:26.950
I think that it's better
if we keep our distance.

340
00:29:34.499 --> 00:29:36.000
I'll see you around.

341
00:30:46.362 --> 00:30:50.450
It's down this way. Come on.

342
00:31:27.529 --> 00:31:29.948
