475
00:46:26.386 --> 00:46:27.053
Relax, dude. Hey, relax.

476
00:46:30.432 --> 00:46:32.434
Whoa! Hey!

477
00:46:34.477 --> 00:46:37.772
Hey, hey, hey, get off!

478
00:46:39.649 --> 00:46:41.484
You're
gonna regret this.

479
00:46:41.609 --> 00:46:44.863
Dude, you're freaking!
What are you doing, man?

480
00:46:48.241 --> 00:46:49.200
- Hardin?
- Hardin?

481
00:47:01.546 --> 00:47:04.215
