485
00:47:59.938 --> 00:48:04.275
Uh, well, it started
about his father

486
00:48:04.359 --> 00:48:08.696
and then your name
sort of came up.

487
00:48:11.408 --> 00:48:12.784
He won't talk to me

488
00:48:12.909 --> 00:48:17.956
so I figured maybe
he would talk to you.

489
00:48:18.081 --> 00:48:19.999
Where is he?

490
00:48:39.185 --> 00:48:41.354
What are you doing here?

491
00:48:41.479 --> 00:48:43.648
I was worried about you.

492
00:48:47.318 --> 00:48:48.611
Shouldn't you be
with your perfect

493
00:48:48.737 --> 00:48:50.155
