511
00:51:51.836 --> 00:51:56.091
You don't ever have to
cover up, not for me.

512
00:53:41.279 --> 00:53:43.573
Hey. You okay?

513
00:53:43.656 --> 00:53:45.075
Yeah.

514
00:53:45.200 --> 00:53:47.118
