you, you didn't answer me.

515
00:53:47.243 --> 00:53:49.996
Um, I'm sorry. My
phone died, I'm sorry.

516
00:53:50.121 --> 00:53:51.623
Where were you?

517
00:53:51.706 --> 00:53:54.834
