of the night?

519
00:54:12.060 --> 00:54:14.062
Noah, I can explain, can we...

520
00:54:16.481 --> 00:54:20.777
Please, can we just...
can we just go inside and talk?

521
00:54:20.860 --> 00:54:22.112
I don't...

522
00:54:22.195 --> 00:54:23.530
No...

523
00:54:23.613 --> 00:54:26.074
I don't believe this.

524
00:54:26.157 --> 00:54:30.203
No, Noah...
Noah, wait.

525
00:54:30.286 --> 00:54:32.997
Noah, I'm...
I'm confused.

526
00:54:33.123 --> 00:54:36.918
I wanted to talk to you
about it for a while.

527
00:54:37.001 --> 00:54:39.504
I am so, so sorry.

528
00:54:47.637 --> 00:54:49.347
Noah...

